  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education Helps to Save Wild Tigers</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education is key to ensuring wild tigers have wild futures. Since 2010 we&apos;ve provided 2200 education packs for children in 25 villages around Bandhavgarh to enable them to go to school.  Rural poverty &amp; the cost of basic books &amp; pens often prevents many children from going to school. Without education their future prospects are bleak, with limited employment options leading to an increased dependency upon the land &amp; further pressure on shrinking tiger habitat. We now want to help 500 more.</narrative>
  </description>
